ssible Maintains up to date knowledge of financial and accounting regulations and best practices Cost Accountant requirements This section should list the essential qualities of an ideal candidate. Include previous work experience, education or achievements that would be beneficial. And list any preferred hard and soft skills. Example Cost Accountant requirements Bachelor\u2019s degree in Accounting or Finance Previous experience in cost accounting an asset Strong attention to detail and analytical thinking skills Superior organizational abilities Excellent communication and interpersonal skills, both written and verbal Minimum of 3 years experience in accounting roles Cost Accountant related job titles: Senior Cost Accountant General Accountant Business Accountant Associate Accountant International Accountant Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
